title: "View on Web" Not working
body:
I've been trying to go into my "View on Web" area of a match whenever I go into my match history, but the only thing that shows up is just a blank page. I have noticed many other posts about this but Riot hasn't responded to any of them, including one posted 4 months ago. Riot, Please message back and tell us how we can fix. And don't make me bring {{champion:119}} into this.
#WelcomeToTheLeagueOfDraven

replies.body: Are you using Microsoft Edge? If yes, Match History doesn't work with Microsoft Edge in Windows 10 version 1511.

Additionally, sometimes [clearing out browser data](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) can resolve the issue. We don't currently have a guide for Edge, so I recommend referring to [this page](https://www.wiknix.com/how-to-clear-cache-and-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-browser/) for directions for Microsoft Edge.
